@NODE 1. "INTRODUCTION"
 With this JIWA Demo program you can write in mode (HIRAGANA, KATAKANA, KANJI).
 This is the new series of JIWA, this program is for all people that study or
 write in japanese using the Amiga computer.
 This program is completely different from the first,it uses public fonts
 JIS16 and JIS24  so,it is not necessary any patch to see the characters.
 In order to install this program just put the JIWA drawer anywhere in your
 HD, don't remove nothing from the drawer.
 
@ENDNODE

