@NODE 14. "TOOLTYPES"


                    In the icon there are two parameters for JIWA:


@{b}1- MAXLINES:@{ub}

               This parameter set the max lines that JIWA use.
               If you have much memory increase this value.
               MAX value is 32768 lines.
          

@{b}2- HELPLINE:@{ub}

           This is the path of the JIWA.guide.


@{b}3- EDICT:@{ub}

           This is the path of the dictionary EDICT.
           @{i}NOT AVAILABLE IN UNREGISTERED VERSION@{ui}
               
@{b}4- KANJIDIC:@{ub}

           This is the path of the dictionary KANJIEDICT.
           @{i}NOT AVAILABLE IN UNREGISTERED VERSION@{ui}

@{b}5- WIDTH-HEIGHT-ID:@{ub}
       
           For display setting.

@{b}6- CHIPSET:@{ub}

           With this select if the program run in AGA or ECS mode.

           TOOLTYPE: @{b}AGA@{ub} or @{b}ECS@{ub}

@{b}7- MENU:@{ub}
             
           Active the JAPANESE or ENGLISH menu

           TOOLTYPE: @{b}JAPANESE@{ub} or @{b}ENGLISH@{ub}


@{b}8- AUTOSAVE:@{ub}
    
           Set the value for autosave of the text.
           
             
@ENDNODE


